'''印尼国家石油公司'''（{{lang-id|Pertamina}}）是[[印度尼西亞|印度尼西亞]]一家国有[[石油|石油]]和[[天然气|天然气]]公司，总部位於[[雅加达|雅加达]]<ref>Useful details about the history of Pertamina are contained in the book about Pertamina by Rhenald Kasali, ''DNA mutation of a powerhouse: Pertamina on the move'', PT Gramedia Pustaka Utama, Jakarta, 2008</ref>。该公司于1968年8月由國家天然氣開發公司（{{lang|id|Pertamin}}，1961年成立）和國家石油開發公司（{{lang|id|Permina}}，1957年成立）合并而成。截至2013年，该公司是印尼第二大[[原油|原油]]生产商，仅次于[[雪佛龍|雪佛龙太平洋印尼公司]]<ref>{{Cite news|first=Amahl S.|author=Azwar|url=http://www.thejakartapost.com/news/2013/06/07/re-elected-ceo-bring-pertamina-number-one.html|title=Re-elected CEO to bring Pertamina to 'number one'|work=The Jakarta Post|date=7 June 2013|accessdate=2021-03-29|archive-date=2018-09-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180928082801/http://www.thejakartapost.com/news/2013/06/07/re-elected-ceo-bring-pertamina-number-one.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2013年，印尼国家石油公司首次登上[[财富世界500强|财富世界500强]]，排名為第122位<ref>{{Cite web|title=Pertamina company profile|url=http://www.indonesia-investments.com/doing-business/indonesian-companies/pertamina/item341|date=25 March 2014|work=Indonesia-investments.com|access-date=2021-03-29|archive-date=2014-09-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140929132519/http://www.indonesia-investments.com/doing-business/indonesian-companies/pertamina/item341|dead-url=no}}</ref>，是唯一一家上榜的印尼企业<ref>{{Cite web|title=Pertamina Masuk Daftar 500 Perusahaan Terbesar Dunia|url=http://bisniskeuangan.kompas.com/read/2013/07/16/1102230/Pertamina.Masuk.Daftar.500.Perusahaan.Terbesar.Dunia|date=16 July 2013|work=Bisinkeuangan.kompas.com|access-date=2021-03-29|archive-date=2013-07-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130721023720/http://bisniskeuangan.kompas.com/read/2013/07/16/1102230/Pertamina.Masuk.Daftar.500.Perusahaan.Terbesar.Dunia|dead-url=no}}</ref>。根据2020年[[财富_(杂志)|财富]]榜单，印尼国家石油公司是印尼最大的公司<ref>{{Cite web|title=Global 500|url=https://fortune.com/global500/2019/|accessdate=2019-07-25|work=Fortune|language=en|archive-date=2019-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191116161250/https://fortune.com/global500/2019/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
